Summary: DECCOLM should clear the screen
Class: bug
Priority: medium
Difficulty: fun
Present-in: 0.53b
Content-type: text/plain

DECCOLM sequences (CSI ? 3 h and CSI ? 3 l) should also clear the screen
and home the cursor.  In PuTTY they don't.  It also appears that they should
reset the scrolling region established by DECSTBM.  I wonder whether there's
anything else they affect.
